<https://w3id.org/emmo/disciplines/units/otherunits> a owl:Ontology ;
    dcterms:abstract """The module 'otherunits' contain non-SI units not included in the 'siacceptedspecialunits', 'siacceptedunits' and 'specialunits' modules. Examples: kBar, ...

